data.description: JUST LIKE NEW! Extremely Well-Cared For & Ready for New Owners ~ This 2020 Home is Located in the Castlerock Community ~ The "Rio Grande" Floor Plan Features 4 BR, 2-1/2 Bath & Extended 2-1/2 Car Garage w/Extra Storage in Overhead Storage Racks ~ Enjoy Lots of Natural Light With High Ceilings in the Living Room & Large Windows ~ Neutral Color Palette & Blinds Throughout ~ Downstairs Master, Study/Office ~ Grand Game Room Up That Opens to Downstairs Living ~ Master Bath is Extended and Features a Super Shower ~ Island Kitchen Has 42" Cabinets w/Pulls & Stainless Appliances ~ The Oversized Laundry Room is Conveniently Located Downstairs ~ Enjoy the Outdoors on a Great Patio  Privacy Fence **Water Softener ,Gas stove , Refrigerator will stay with the home**~also when owner purchased the home he chose top quality ugrades for and through out the home** Seller is offering 5k toward closing cost or interest rate buy down
